Class
Description
Aeroport
The Aeroport class represents an airport with specific attributes such as its name, address, and associated department.
Annee
The Annee class represents a year with specific attributes such as the year itself and the inflation rate.
Commune
The Commune class represents a municipality with specific attributes such as its ID, name, associated department, and neighboring municipalities.

Departement
The Departement class represents a department with specific attributes such as its ID, name, and cultural investment for the year 2019.
DonneesAnnuelles
The DonneesAnnuelles class represents annual data for a specific municipality and year.
Gare
The Gare class represents a train station with specific attributes such as its code, name, type (freight or passenger), and associated municipality.
